- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is another possible category as the paper discusses formal semantics, which is related to logic.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of formal semantics in modeling and analyzing software systems, which is related to AI.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is another possible category as the paper discusses formal semantics, which is related to formal languages and automata theory.
